Steps to setup python in eclipse

On winodws -> preference -> pythoninterpreter -> provide the interpreter from C Drive python installation path
Later, Configure HADOOP_HOME and SPARK_HOME for python - pyDev Environment.
On Libraries, select pySpark and py4j libraries and add it. --This would add these two libraries into System libraries of PYTHON environment.

Example link:
https://blog.puneethabm.com/pyspark-dev-set-up-eclipse-windows/

Once everything is setup, Create python project and run the code.
